Prior to all analyses, the mean was subtracted from mediolateral and anterioposterior COP trajectories, which transformed the original time series into x and y time series, respectively. Subsequently, x and y time series were bi-directionally filtered (second-order low-pass Butterworth filter, cut-off frequency 12.5 Hz) and the resultant distance time series r was constructed using 
