\begin{document}$$ {\text{SP}} = {\sum\limits_{i = 1}^{N - 1} {{\sqrt {(x_{{i + 1}} - x_{i} )^{2} + (y_{{i + 1}} - y_{i} )^{2} } }} } $$\end{document}.
